content: 20 多年来，海滩俱乐部一直是电子音乐爱好者的首选目的地。 可容纳10,000多人，是北美最大的户外综合体。 海滩俱乐部每个周末都会邀请伟大的艺术家，以其在电子音乐行业中的国际声誉而自豪。
contentEn: The Beachclub has been a top destination for electronic music enthusiasts for over 20 years. With a capacity of more than 10,000 people, it is the biggest outdoor complex in North America. Featuring great artists every weekend the Beachclub prides itself on its international reputation within the electronic music industry.
